WEBVTT

00:13.830 --> 00:15.940
[Ziji Palace]

00:15.430 --> 00:16.390
Empress Dowager,

00:16.390 --> 00:18.640
you must seek justice for us.

00:22.440 --> 00:23.350
Why are you crying?

00:23.350 --> 00:24.550
Xiao Wuyi is back.

00:24.570 --> 00:26.320
Didn't he die in battle at Jiuzhang Plain?

00:26.320 --> 00:27.390
The news is fake.

00:27.390 --> 00:28.600
He is perfectly alive.

00:28.600 --> 00:30.830
This morning,
he even led troops to my Lantai gathering.

00:30.830 --> 00:32.240
Adjutant Chen and Vice Minister Wei

00:32.240 --> 00:34.840
just refused to write poems
praising his achievements,

00:34.840 --> 00:36.520
and he had them killed on the spot.

00:36.520 --> 00:38.880
Xiao Wuyi brought troops
into the capital without an edict

00:38.880 --> 00:40.110
and wrongfully killed court officials.

00:40.110 --> 00:41.110
This is treason!

00:41.390 --> 00:42.670
This is treason!

00:42.670 --> 00:44.330
Did he bring his army back too?

00:44.640 --> 00:45.350
Not quite.

00:49.030 --> 00:51.430
It's fine if he didn't
bring the army back.

00:51.560 --> 00:53.390
After all, Xiao Wuyi's wife,
the Crown Princess,

00:53.390 --> 00:54.350
is my niece.

00:54.600 --> 00:57.520
I'm sure that Lord Xiao and his son
remain loyal to His Majesty.

00:57.520 --> 00:58.560
Aunt,

00:58.880 --> 01:00.810
can a mere marriage prove loyalty?

01:01.000 --> 01:02.880
Xiao Wuyi can kill officials at will now,

01:02.880 --> 01:03.750
with no regard for the law.

01:03.750 --> 01:05.710
His wild ambitions are obvious.

01:10.400 --> 01:12.000
Now that His Majesty is unwell,

01:12.000 --> 01:13.950
the court is unstable
and people are panicking.

01:13.950 --> 01:15.200
If at this time,

01:15.510 --> 01:17.680
Xiao Wuyi commands his troops
and declares himself ruler,

01:17.680 --> 01:20.200
you and His Majesty will be sitting ducks.

01:20.400 --> 01:21.600
Then in your opinion,

01:21.760 --> 01:22.789
what should we do?

01:23.230 --> 01:25.560
Give me the imperial guards
so we can prepare early.

01:25.560 --> 01:26.760
Let's strike first

01:27.200 --> 01:28.530
and get rid of Xiao Wuyi.

01:34.950 --> 01:37.120
Aunt, there is no time to hesitate.

01:37.400 --> 01:38.870
We are family after all.

01:39.310 --> 01:40.310
Empress Dowager!

01:41.229 --> 01:41.970
Empress Dowager!

01:41.970 --> 01:43.759
His Majesty has coughed up blood
and fainted again.

01:43.759 --> 01:44.430
My son!

01:45.950 --> 01:48.120
Summon the royal physician!

01:50.400 --> 01:51.710
This old fox

01:53.200 --> 01:55.120
refuses to name me Crown Prince

01:56.320 --> 01:58.720
and won't even give me military authority.

01:59.560 --> 02:01.710
She's only ever used me as a shield.

02:08.150 --> 02:10.080
So you all want to use me as a pawn?

02:12.390 --> 02:14.790
Then don't blame me
for flipping the board.

03:41.740 --> 03:45.550
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:46.020 --> 03:48.470
[Episode 2]

03:52.750 --> 03:54.870
The Crown Princess doesn't like to go out.

03:54.870 --> 03:55.870
She likes to read.

03:56.079 --> 03:57.400
Her favorite is Mencius,

03:57.400 --> 03:58.870
she doesn't like Laozi and Zhuangzi,

03:58.870 --> 04:00.960
and she is quite familiar with
Buddhist scriptures.

04:00.960 --> 04:02.190
If you want to know more about her,

04:02.190 --> 04:04.320
you can start with the books she likes.

04:07.710 --> 04:08.910
You haven't been back

04:10.000 --> 04:10.930
for these years.

04:11.360 --> 04:13.290
The Crown Princess doesn't say it,

04:13.310 --> 04:14.910
but she misses you very much.

04:15.190 --> 04:17.390
She's always in Jinyi Courtyard

04:17.600 --> 04:20.060
praying for your safety
on the battlefield.

04:20.310 --> 04:21.110
Although Ziqi

04:21.390 --> 04:22.720
is Madam Rui's son,

04:22.870 --> 04:25.730
the Crown Princess
has always taken good care of him

04:25.750 --> 04:27.140
and taught him carefully.

04:27.140 --> 04:28.870
You should thank her properly.

04:30.870 --> 04:32.400
Your Highness, I found out.

04:34.310 --> 04:36.260
The stalls of the Young Master of Miraculous Craft
at the Lantai gathering

04:36.260 --> 04:38.360
were all set up
by the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

04:38.360 --> 04:39.290
Grand Tutor Xie?

04:40.659 --> 04:42.360
That lady is Grand Tutor Xie's daughter.

04:42.360 --> 04:44.120
If Grand Tutor Xie only has one daughter,

04:44.120 --> 04:44.920
then it's her.

04:48.830 --> 04:50.270
There is a rumor in the capital

04:50.270 --> 04:52.520
that Prince Changsha is about to
marry the Grand Tutor's daughter.

04:52.520 --> 04:54.560
The betrothal gifts have been sent to
the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

04:54.560 --> 04:56.870
Does the Grand Tutor
also support Prince Changsha?

04:56.870 --> 04:59.670
I am looking forward to
this wedding more and more.

05:01.620 --> 05:04.080
Wuyi, I am talking about
the Crown Princess!

05:10.460 --> 05:12.330
Since you know the Crown Princess so well,

05:12.330 --> 05:13.860
why didn't you marry her
yourself back then?

05:13.860 --> 05:14.300
You!

05:16.630 --> 05:17.560
Crown Princess.

05:20.070 --> 05:21.600
Greetings, Your Highness.

05:22.080 --> 05:23.740
So you are the Crown Princess?

05:24.460 --> 05:25.140
Yes, I am.

05:29.090 --> 05:30.020
Nice to meet you.

05:30.320 --> 05:32.180
Thank you for your efforts today.

05:56.620 --> 05:58.090
The Beifu pretended to be defeated

05:58.090 --> 05:59.600
and lured the enemy into the city,

05:59.600 --> 06:01.830
then surrounded them
and wiped most of them out.

06:01.830 --> 06:03.720
The entire Eastern Army
of Northern Qin has been wiped out,

06:03.720 --> 06:05.360
and the Five-City territory
has been reclaimed.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.800
The remaining enemy forces fled in defeat.

06:06.800 --> 06:09.260
Here is the roster
of meritorious soldiers,

06:09.510 --> 06:11.370
awaiting Your Majesty's reward.

06:15.560 --> 06:18.160
I want to impeach Xiao Wuyi,
the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

06:18.160 --> 06:19.240
At yesterday's Lantai gathering,

06:19.240 --> 06:20.920
Xiao Wuyi blatantly disregarded
the laws of the state

06:20.920 --> 06:22.680
and murdered Chen Guangtong,
the Military Advisor,

06:22.680 --> 06:25.270
and Wei Qianli,
the Household Department Adjutant.

06:25.270 --> 06:27.480
I second that. I second that.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.630
I second that!

06:30.070 --> 06:31.070
Empress Dowager,

06:31.160 --> 06:32.750
Chen Guangtong
leaked military intelligence,

06:32.750 --> 06:34.510
delayed military operations,
and held up provisions.

06:34.510 --> 06:36.000
Vice Minister Wei,
who oversaw military equipment,

06:36.000 --> 06:37.950
passed off inferior goods
and embezzled military funds.

06:37.950 --> 06:39.950
The two men were guilty
of countless crimes.

06:39.950 --> 06:40.950
Unable to face punishment,
they took their own lives.

06:40.950 --> 06:41.880
Here are years of

06:41.920 --> 06:43.510
correspondence

06:43.630 --> 06:44.680
and records of embezzlement.

06:44.680 --> 06:46.159
Please investigate thoroughly,
Your Majesties.

06:46.159 --> 06:46.870
Shameless!

06:47.159 --> 06:48.070
Everyone in the court

06:48.070 --> 06:49.800
knows you killed Adjutant Chen
and Vice Minister Wei yourself

06:49.800 --> 06:51.830
at the Lantai gathering!

06:51.830 --> 06:55.290
Yesterday's poetry gathering
was hosted by Prince Changsha.

06:55.560 --> 06:57.000
Everyone knows

06:57.000 --> 06:58.830
that Prince Changsha
is the future Crown Prince.

06:58.830 --> 07:01.160
How would I dare commit murder
in front of His Highness?

07:01.160 --> 07:02.830
That would only embarrass His Highness.

07:02.830 --> 07:05.920
Your Highness, were these two killed by me

07:06.360 --> 07:07.920
or did they commit suicide out of guilt?

07:07.920 --> 07:10.050
They took their own lives out of guilt.

07:11.240 --> 07:12.700
Thank you, Your Highness,

07:12.870 --> 07:14.160
for clearing my name.

07:14.400 --> 07:16.230
I naturally believe in Young Lord Xiao.

07:16.230 --> 07:18.560
Young Lord Xiao has worked hard
defending the territory over the years.

07:18.560 --> 07:19.750
With numerous military achievements,

07:19.750 --> 07:22.010
he should be well rewarded and promoted.

07:22.190 --> 07:22.680
You...

07:22.680 --> 07:24.060
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

07:24.060 --> 07:26.360
I dare not decline the rewards
meant for the soldiers.

07:26.360 --> 07:28.800
I don't seek promotion for myself;

07:28.920 --> 07:30.320
I only ask for one person.

07:30.950 --> 07:32.110
Please grant me permission to marry,
Empress Dowager.

07:32.110 --> 07:33.890
I am willing to marry the
daughter of Grand Tutor Xie

07:33.890 --> 07:36.020
with the rites of a principal consort.

07:51.000 --> 07:51.730
Grand Tutor.

07:52.120 --> 07:53.310
The Empress Dowager is unwell

07:53.310 --> 07:54.620
and will not see anyone today.

07:54.620 --> 07:55.600
She has sent you a food box

07:55.600 --> 07:57.260
and asked you to return early.

07:57.720 --> 07:58.360
Eunuch He,

07:58.690 --> 08:01.130
please deliver another message
to the Empress Dowager for me.

08:01.130 --> 08:01.850
Grand Tutor,

08:01.850 --> 08:04.190
I cannot take any more messages
for you today.

08:04.190 --> 08:06.330
Is this the Empress Dowager's intention?

08:06.330 --> 08:09.160
The Empress Dowager often says:
Enemies surround us on all sides.

08:09.160 --> 08:10.680
Within the court,
there is Prince Changsha;

08:10.680 --> 08:12.270
beyond it, there is the Beifu Army.

08:12.270 --> 08:13.890
Young Lord Xiao holds military power

08:13.890 --> 08:15.040
and his achievements shake the realm.

08:15.040 --> 08:17.370
Only the Beifu Army
can defend the northern border.

08:17.370 --> 08:19.970
The Emperor and I
sit on the throne helplessly,

08:20.060 --> 08:21.450
with no way out.

08:23.730 --> 08:25.130
Mind your words, Eunuch.

08:27.540 --> 08:28.270
Grand Tutor,

08:31.540 --> 08:34.789
the Empress Dowager understands
a father's love for his child.

08:34.789 --> 08:36.200
She only hopes the Grand Tutor

08:36.200 --> 08:39.080
might also understand
a mother's love for hers.

08:39.480 --> 08:40.280
I understand.

08:41.360 --> 08:42.030
I

08:42.909 --> 08:44.440
accept the imperial edict.

08:44.690 --> 08:46.020
Thank you for the grace.

08:48.790 --> 08:50.850
But this jade must be quite valuable.

08:51.650 --> 08:53.040
Fine jade suits a gentleman.

08:53.040 --> 08:54.820
Mao is the best gentleman in the world.

08:54.820 --> 08:56.720
He naturally deserves the best jade.

08:56.720 --> 08:57.720
Don't frown.

08:57.750 --> 08:59.550
Didn't Mao say he'd be back soon?

08:59.600 --> 09:00.730
You should be happy.

09:01.000 --> 09:01.600
True.

09:01.790 --> 09:04.720
Brother said he had prepared surprises
for all of us.

09:06.510 --> 09:07.240
Father,

09:07.540 --> 09:08.110
Mother.

09:11.380 --> 09:13.570
I didn't do anything wrong, did I?

09:16.440 --> 09:17.750
I really didn't do anything.

09:17.750 --> 09:19.510
I made this myself.

09:29.240 --> 09:31.440
Lady Xie, receive the imperial decree!

09:33.790 --> 09:34.750
I'm really going to hang myself.

09:34.750 --> 09:35.840
-No, no, no.
-Don't try to stop me, anyone.

09:35.840 --> 09:37.270
-My Lady, come down.
-I'm going to hang myself.

09:37.270 --> 09:38.450
My Lady, stop making
a scene and come down.

09:38.450 --> 09:39.970
Darling, this...

09:44.360 --> 09:45.030
Father,

09:45.230 --> 09:46.750
Xiao Wuyi killed two courtiers

09:46.750 --> 09:47.510
in front of so many people

09:47.510 --> 09:48.910
at the Lantai gathering.

09:49.030 --> 09:50.080
If I marry him,

09:50.230 --> 09:51.000
in a few days,

09:51.000 --> 09:52.670
you'll have to collect my corpse.

09:52.670 --> 09:53.480
If that's the case,

09:53.480 --> 09:55.540
I might as well hang myself right now.

10:01.360 --> 10:02.390
I'm really not joking.

10:02.390 --> 10:03.120
I'm hanging myself now!

10:03.120 --> 10:04.250
I'm hanging myself.

10:04.320 --> 10:04.630
My Lady!

10:04.630 --> 10:06.140
Why not switch to a hemp rope?

10:06.140 --> 10:07.020
It's sturdier.

10:12.760 --> 10:15.160
This is your favorite
white porcelain teacup,

10:15.160 --> 10:16.040
given by Lejun.

10:19.020 --> 10:20.810
This is the incense burner
you made yourself,

10:20.810 --> 10:22.540
which was fired for three days.

10:27.190 --> 10:28.360
This is a treasure box

10:28.360 --> 10:30.290
made of golden-thread nanmu wood.

10:32.070 --> 10:32.960
This is nice.

10:47.280 --> 10:49.610
The palace has issued the imperial edict.

10:49.790 --> 10:51.390
Do you want to defy it?

10:54.720 --> 10:55.480
Yao Yao,

10:56.840 --> 10:59.840
the Empress Dowager
has long known that Prince Changsha

10:59.840 --> 11:02.260
wants to marry you,
and she knows I have always refused.

11:02.260 --> 11:04.140
With Young Lord Xiao stepping in,

11:04.350 --> 11:07.320
the Empress Dowager agreed to
the marriage without hesitation.

11:07.320 --> 11:08.400
Do you know why?

11:11.190 --> 11:14.560
The fiercer the fight between
Prince Jing'an's Mansion
and Prince Changsha gets,

11:14.560 --> 11:16.680
the safer it is for the frail

11:16.700 --> 11:18.560
Emperor and the Empress Dowager.

11:18.670 --> 11:20.320
When the snipe and the clam grapple,

11:20.320 --> 11:21.650
the fisherman profits.

11:23.060 --> 11:24.460
Your marriage is nothing

11:25.730 --> 11:28.780
more than a pawn
in the struggle for power.

11:29.830 --> 11:31.380
Then let whoever wants to
be that pawn take their place.

11:31.380 --> 11:32.050
I won't.

11:32.270 --> 11:33.640
The Empress Dowager's own niece

11:33.640 --> 11:35.170
has been married into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion for years,

11:35.170 --> 11:36.760
and Young Lord Xiao
doesn't even recognize her.

11:36.760 --> 11:38.240
If I marry into that family,

11:38.240 --> 11:39.630
and end up like the Crown Princess,

11:39.630 --> 11:40.690
then every day I...

11:41.440 --> 11:42.570
Isn't that perfect?

11:44.670 --> 11:46.120
You don't like him anyway.

11:46.120 --> 11:48.240
Young Lord Xiao is away on expeditions,

11:48.240 --> 11:50.440
and you'd be alone in the manor every day.

11:50.440 --> 11:51.440
By then,

11:51.470 --> 11:53.600
you can build waterwheels if you want,

11:53.610 --> 11:55.610
or fire white porcelain if you want.

11:55.630 --> 11:57.340
No one will control you anymore.

11:57.340 --> 11:59.470
Isn't this the life you've dreamed of?

12:05.050 --> 12:06.470
Since it's a foregone conclusion,

12:06.470 --> 12:08.730
stop letting your imagination run wild.

12:09.540 --> 12:12.000
Who you marry
doesn't make much difference.

12:17.950 --> 12:18.880
No, Mother.

12:18.910 --> 12:20.030
I want to marry Mao.

12:21.280 --> 12:21.670
I...

12:22.490 --> 12:23.090
Father,

12:23.120 --> 12:24.480
I want to marry Mao.

12:24.480 --> 12:25.240
-Fine.
-I...

12:25.650 --> 12:26.450
I understand.

12:26.510 --> 12:27.480
No, you don't.

12:27.540 --> 12:28.820
I want to marry Mao.

12:33.030 --> 12:35.790
I hear that the daughter
of Grand Tutor Xie Huaigui,

12:35.790 --> 12:37.030
from a distinguished family,

12:37.030 --> 12:38.550
has been granted in marriage
by the Empress Dowager

12:38.550 --> 12:41.000
to Young Lord Xiao
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

12:41.000 --> 12:43.190
The wedding will be held on
an auspicious day.

12:43.190 --> 12:45.450
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

12:47.320 --> 12:48.480
Congratulations, Your Highness.

12:48.480 --> 12:50.410
Congratulations, Your Highness.

12:57.550 --> 12:58.450
Thank you for your hard work, Eunuch.

12:58.450 --> 13:00.380
You flatter me, Crown Princess.

13:00.870 --> 13:01.800
The Empress Dowager said

13:01.800 --> 13:03.460
that you are one of the family.

13:03.600 --> 13:04.800
Please rest assured.

13:05.800 --> 13:06.980
May the Empress Dowager enjoy good health.

13:06.980 --> 13:07.820
I understand.

13:08.160 --> 13:11.090
Lady Xie will also
be part of our family in the future.

13:11.200 --> 13:13.360
I will take my leave now.

13:20.270 --> 13:22.270
You've worked hard, Your Highness.

13:22.880 --> 13:24.810
Then the details of the wedding...

13:25.240 --> 13:26.370
Please don't worry.

13:26.460 --> 13:27.860
It is my duty.

13:29.390 --> 13:30.000
Great.

13:31.710 --> 13:32.280
Wuyi,

13:33.900 --> 13:35.030
where are you going?

13:35.910 --> 13:37.320
I heard there's a hot spring
in the western suburbs.

13:37.320 --> 13:38.320
It's rare for me to return to the capital,

13:38.320 --> 13:39.910
so I want to enjoy the hot spring.

13:39.910 --> 13:41.240
Are you interested too?

13:56.440 --> 13:58.350
Since it's your first meeting
with the Crown Princess today,

13:58.350 --> 13:59.730
are you already leaving?

13:59.730 --> 14:01.260
Crown Princess, could it be

14:01.260 --> 14:02.790
that you want to come along?

14:03.990 --> 14:06.000
Are your clothes packed?

14:07.000 --> 14:08.480
Ruisheng has prepared them.

14:08.480 --> 14:09.240
Then,

14:09.800 --> 14:11.260
farewell, Your Highness.

14:18.270 --> 14:20.160
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

14:19.820 --> 14:20.460
Nanxing!

14:24.910 --> 14:25.870
The Young Lady ran away!

14:25.770 --> 14:28.690
[For Lejun, to be opened personally]

14:33.050 --> 14:35.440
Is Granny, who is half-blind,
feeling better?

14:35.440 --> 14:38.670
Thank you for your concern, My Lady.
She's still in good shape.

14:38.670 --> 14:42.200
Then I'll leave the trip to Yongzhou
in your hands and Granny's.

14:53.320 --> 14:55.630
I thought you were really here
for the hot spring.

14:55.630 --> 14:56.870
Is everything arranged?

14:56.870 --> 14:57.730
Rest assured, Your Highness.

14:57.730 --> 15:00.060
Madam Rui has taken the dancers
to the hot spring villa.

15:00.060 --> 15:01.320
With all the singing and dancing,

15:01.320 --> 15:02.450
even if someone asks,

15:02.450 --> 15:04.780
I guarantee no one
will know where you are.

15:05.370 --> 15:06.230
Your Highness,

15:06.620 --> 15:09.550
something is wrong
with the two villages near the ferry.

15:09.550 --> 15:10.680
What's suspicious?

15:11.060 --> 15:11.920
Their accents.

15:12.510 --> 15:14.560
The villagers don't sound like
they are from the suburbs.

15:14.560 --> 15:16.070
And the fields are abandoned.

15:16.070 --> 15:18.000
The crops haven't been watered for days.

15:18.000 --> 15:19.600
More men or women?

15:20.080 --> 15:21.750
More able-bodied adults,
or more elderly people and children?

15:21.750 --> 15:22.840
More able-bodied men.

15:22.840 --> 15:24.300
I haven't seen many women.

15:27.600 --> 15:28.600
That makes sense.

15:28.670 --> 15:29.910
But in this world,

15:30.320 --> 15:32.450
how can a village only have strong men?

15:32.870 --> 15:33.630
Qing Long,

15:34.270 --> 15:36.130
how is your reading going lately?

15:37.330 --> 15:38.460
I haven't read much.

15:39.480 --> 15:40.390
Do you know what

15:40.840 --> 15:41.720
"replacing the old with the new,

15:41.720 --> 15:42.910
moving things under cover,

15:42.910 --> 15:45.510
and swapping the heavens and the earth"
means?

15:47.750 --> 15:50.440
You mean these villagers are
all impostors?

15:51.200 --> 15:52.840
What about the original villagers?

15:52.840 --> 15:54.040
Were they all killed?

15:55.200 --> 15:56.200
Who would do this?

15:57.840 --> 15:59.100
It's Prince Changsha.

15:59.360 --> 16:01.320
-He's trying to seize control of
the river transport routes.
-Prince Changsha...

16:01.320 --> 16:04.080
Then the nearby granaries
must be controlled too.

16:04.080 --> 16:05.120
Prince Changsha's appetite

16:05.120 --> 16:07.380
goes far beyond the ferry and granaries.

16:08.240 --> 16:10.240
What he wants is the entire capital.

16:11.390 --> 16:12.520
The entire capital?

16:13.030 --> 16:14.200
If I am not mistaken,

16:14.510 --> 16:16.670
the villages, mountains, forests,

16:17.080 --> 16:18.410
ferries, and granaries

16:18.750 --> 16:21.550
are already filled with
his troops and assassins.

16:22.700 --> 16:24.580
He is even faster than I expected.

16:27.380 --> 16:28.910
Slow down.
The things inside are very expensive.

16:28.910 --> 16:29.200
Okay.

16:29.200 --> 16:29.860
Be careful.

16:29.960 --> 16:31.960
Why does this lady look so familiar?

16:32.910 --> 16:34.320
Put this one in there.

16:35.290 --> 16:37.090
It's the one from the Xie family.

16:37.240 --> 16:38.360
It's Consort Xie.

16:39.240 --> 16:40.720
Why is she getting on a boat?

16:40.720 --> 16:42.250
Isn't she getting married?

16:50.170 --> 16:52.480
A hidden dragon lingers in quiet grace,

16:53.360 --> 16:55.820
a soaring wild goose
echoes in the distance.

16:56.390 --> 16:57.450
Above the thin sky…

16:58.510 --> 16:59.960
What comes next?

17:00.790 --> 17:02.480
Above the thin sky,
I feel ashamed like drifting clouds;

17:02.480 --> 17:04.339
by the riverbank, I stand humbled
before the deep abyss.

17:04.339 --> 17:05.920
In pursuing virtue,
I lack the wisdom for it.

17:05.920 --> 17:08.240
As for retreating to farming,
I lack the strength for that either.

17:08.240 --> 17:10.500
Miss, you recited the poem incorrectly.

17:10.869 --> 17:13.829
This poem is about Xie Lingyun
recovering from a long illness,

17:13.829 --> 17:16.290
climbing a tower
and gazing afar, expressing his feelings.

17:16.290 --> 17:18.720
It vents his frustration
over his political failure.

17:18.720 --> 17:20.060
Since you are not an official,

17:20.060 --> 17:22.160
it's inappropriate for you
to recite this poem.

17:22.160 --> 17:23.270
You think you know everything.

17:23.270 --> 17:24.720
Such a pretty face,

17:25.000 --> 17:26.960
and yet you can't keep your mouth shut.

17:26.960 --> 17:27.680
Who are you?

17:28.160 --> 17:29.160
You don't know me?

17:29.440 --> 17:30.750
You have a lot of nerve.

17:31.070 --> 17:32.270
Why should I know you?

17:33.270 --> 17:34.730
So she doesn't know me yet.

17:37.510 --> 17:39.170
May I know your surname, miss?

17:39.350 --> 17:40.480
Where are you going?

17:44.750 --> 17:46.550
None of your business.

17:47.550 --> 17:48.830
Such a pretty face,

17:49.060 --> 17:50.980
and yet you can't keep your mouth shut.

17:50.980 --> 17:51.910
What did you say?

17:52.930 --> 17:54.550
Boatman, who is this man?

17:54.550 --> 17:56.350
Why is he on the boat I chartered?

18:14.350 --> 18:14.880
You!

18:25.920 --> 18:27.650
Why did you pull your hand back?

18:28.160 --> 18:29.420
Men and women should not
have physical contact.

18:29.420 --> 18:30.830
Then why did you reach out
in the first place?

18:30.830 --> 18:32.870
Saving one life is worth
more than building a seven-story pagoda.

18:32.870 --> 18:34.880
So what does it mean to only save half
and then stop?

18:34.880 --> 18:36.490
I realized you weren't going to
die anyway.

18:36.490 --> 18:37.550
Rules matter more.

18:38.110 --> 18:38.680
Fine.

18:39.350 --> 18:40.510
You, I...

18:41.680 --> 18:43.270
Boatman, who is this?

18:43.270 --> 18:44.480
Why is he on my boat?

18:48.550 --> 18:49.960
How's today's "fat sheep" doing?

18:49.960 --> 18:51.070
Very good.

18:56.490 --> 18:57.890
Which young lady is this,

18:58.080 --> 19:00.030
traveling alone

19:00.410 --> 19:01.620
with so much gold and silver?

19:01.620 --> 19:02.690
An eloped bride.

19:03.070 --> 19:05.830
The half-blind man
said she was going to Yongzhou.

19:05.830 --> 19:07.110
Once she's on my boat,

19:07.510 --> 19:08.590
where it goes

19:09.310 --> 19:11.030
is not up to her.

19:12.640 --> 19:13.350
Boatman!

19:13.790 --> 19:15.520
This is not how you do business.

19:16.880 --> 19:17.810
Is anyone there?

19:18.720 --> 19:20.240
Where did everyone go?

19:22.830 --> 19:24.160
What? It stinks.

19:27.110 --> 19:27.830
Boatman.

19:31.830 --> 19:32.750
Tung oil?

19:37.000 --> 19:37.590
Let me go!

19:46.790 --> 19:48.320
Why are there so many women?

19:50.160 --> 19:50.840
Wait.

19:51.240 --> 19:52.350
You're untying them without even asking?

19:52.350 --> 19:53.070
Ask what?

19:53.090 --> 19:54.420
This is obviously a suspicious boat.

19:54.420 --> 19:56.420
Could they have tied themselves up?

19:58.890 --> 19:59.500
Who is it?

20:01.770 --> 20:03.370
Which blind bastard is this?

20:07.920 --> 20:08.750
Beast!

20:10.310 --> 20:11.240
I'll blow you up!

20:19.000 --> 20:19.350
You!

20:20.030 --> 20:21.310
Wait a minute.

20:33.380 --> 20:35.010
How dare you traffic people!

20:36.240 --> 20:37.970
Go with me to see the officials.

20:39.070 --> 20:39.920
Get up.

20:42.140 --> 20:43.270
Report to the officials?

20:43.270 --> 20:44.270
Which officials?

20:44.640 --> 20:45.820
The Capital Prefect!

20:45.820 --> 20:47.350
And who's the complainant?

20:47.920 --> 20:48.550
Me.

20:48.680 --> 20:49.600
And who are you?

20:51.750 --> 20:54.210
Forget it, I'll go find
the ferry officials.

20:55.440 --> 20:56.570
Where are you going?

20:56.830 --> 20:57.750
Little lady,

20:58.200 --> 20:59.790
curiosity

21:00.400 --> 21:02.070
can get you killed.

21:02.790 --> 21:04.450
I do know a bit of martial arts.

21:04.820 --> 21:05.680
Stay behind me.

21:11.190 --> 21:12.780
Such a pretty face.

21:13.920 --> 21:14.920
What a pity.

21:15.270 --> 21:17.480
Where are those martial arts skills
of yours?

21:17.480 --> 21:18.610
I only know a little.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.720
Where is your hidden weapon?

21:20.720 --> 21:21.480
Use it.

21:22.030 --> 21:23.310
I'm out. I only had two.

21:34.480 --> 21:35.310
He...

21:35.310 --> 21:36.640
Heroine, spare my life!

21:37.720 --> 21:38.720
Do you surrender?

21:40.350 --> 21:41.150
Spare my life!

21:45.350 --> 21:46.210
Your Highness,

21:46.510 --> 21:47.370
Jiayu ran away.

21:52.780 --> 21:54.180
So she actually got away.

21:54.590 --> 21:57.190
We should hurry
and send someone to find Jiayu.

21:57.550 --> 21:59.480
Jiayu most likely went to Yongzhou

21:59.590 --> 22:01.390
to find your brother, Prince Qi.

22:01.880 --> 22:03.810
Why do you want me to bring her back?

22:04.750 --> 22:06.680
Don't you want them to be together?

22:06.720 --> 22:07.720
Of course I hope

22:07.720 --> 22:10.030
my brother and Jiayu
can eventually end up together.

22:10.030 --> 22:11.960
But Jiayu grew up in the capital.

22:12.270 --> 22:14.550
The farthest she's ever been
is the outskirts of the capital.

22:14.550 --> 22:16.350
If Jiayu goes to Yongzhou alone,

22:16.440 --> 22:18.550
something will definitely happen to her.

22:18.550 --> 22:19.880
Nanxing, come here.

22:26.750 --> 22:27.790
Yes, Your Highness.

22:27.790 --> 22:28.990
I'll do it right away.

22:29.030 --> 22:31.110
I'm a legitimate merchant.

22:31.790 --> 22:32.750
For no reason at all,

22:32.750 --> 22:35.300
I was kidnapped
and brought here by this demoness.

22:35.300 --> 22:38.190
My Lord, you must give me justice.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.810
What are you looking at?

22:48.400 --> 22:51.240
This boatman traffics people
and abducts innocent women.

22:51.240 --> 22:52.400
You're the ferry official here.

22:52.400 --> 22:54.270
Such a heartless thing has happened,

22:54.270 --> 22:55.960
so you won't be able to escape either.

22:55.960 --> 22:56.830
Who are you?

22:58.310 --> 22:59.480
I am a passenger.

23:00.350 --> 23:01.920
By the way, I also have a few chests.

23:01.920 --> 23:02.850
They were also taken by them.

23:02.850 --> 23:04.580
You have to get them back for me.

23:06.590 --> 23:07.160
And you?

23:08.640 --> 23:10.700
He was fighting with me over the boat.

23:10.920 --> 23:12.240
He took so much of my money

23:12.240 --> 23:14.110
and sold the same boat to two people.

23:14.110 --> 23:14.830
So corrupt.

23:14.870 --> 23:16.270
Who sold it to two people?

23:16.400 --> 23:17.920
I don't even know him!

23:18.220 --> 23:20.270
If you aren't here to fight for the boat,

23:20.270 --> 23:21.680
then what are you here for?

23:21.680 --> 23:22.270
I...

23:23.200 --> 23:25.330
I came to do business with the boatman.

23:26.640 --> 23:28.200
The business didn't go through,

23:28.200 --> 23:29.800
but I got to watch a good show.

23:32.980 --> 23:34.400
You don't need to look at him.

23:34.400 --> 23:36.130
Now I've brought the man to you.

23:36.390 --> 23:37.720
Report it to the authorities
if you have to.

23:37.720 --> 23:38.450
Report what?

23:39.000 --> 23:40.000
You just said

23:41.030 --> 23:42.160
someone was seized?

23:46.680 --> 23:47.940
Did someone bully you?

23:49.480 --> 23:50.410
Don't be afraid.

23:50.440 --> 23:51.720
Just tell us

23:51.720 --> 23:52.750
what he did to you earlier.

23:52.750 --> 23:54.880
Someone is here to stand up for you now.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.110
I...

23:58.270 --> 23:58.960
I...

23:59.420 --> 24:00.820
I came of my own free will.

24:00.980 --> 24:03.110
My sister and I both signed contracts.

24:03.150 --> 24:04.080
No one forced me.

24:04.280 --> 24:04.880
No one.

24:06.110 --> 24:07.240
Then what about her?

24:07.720 --> 24:08.310
Her?

24:09.160 --> 24:10.310
She's the human trafficker.

24:10.310 --> 24:12.200
She has hidden weapons
and knows martial arts!

24:12.200 --> 24:13.790
Wait, what are you talking about?

24:13.790 --> 24:15.110
I'm a human trafficker?

24:15.110 --> 24:15.970
I just saved...

24:16.260 --> 24:17.370
You have to testify for me.

24:17.370 --> 24:19.300
I was obviously trying to save her.

24:22.680 --> 24:23.400
You...

24:24.140 --> 24:25.370
You're in this together.

24:25.370 --> 24:26.170
Take her down.

24:27.480 --> 24:28.030
Wait.

24:29.640 --> 24:31.770
Since the trafficker has been caught,

24:37.790 --> 24:40.120
it's time to talk about our business.

24:40.770 --> 24:41.380
Okay.

24:43.110 --> 24:43.640
Let's go.

24:44.590 --> 24:45.310
Let me go.

24:45.840 --> 24:46.920
Let me go!

24:49.790 --> 24:50.450
Get inside.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.030
Behave.

25:04.050 --> 25:04.620
Run!

25:18.310 --> 25:20.270
A hidden dragon lingers in quiet grace,

25:20.270 --> 25:22.270
a soaring wild goose
echoes in the distance.

25:22.270 --> 25:24.560
Above the thin sky,
I feel ashamed like drifting clouds;

25:24.560 --> 25:26.640
In pursuing virtue,
I lack the wisdom for it.

25:26.640 --> 25:30.300
As for retreating to farming,
I lack the strength for that either.

25:33.030 --> 25:34.830
You're taking credit for my work again.

25:34.830 --> 25:37.440
Cut the crap.
How many hidden sentries are left?

25:37.440 --> 25:38.750
There are two left in the northeast.

25:38.750 --> 25:39.920
His Highness is still injured.

25:39.920 --> 25:41.200
A fight might not be to our advantage.

25:41.200 --> 25:42.730
Let's finish this quickly.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.580
If His Highness
hadn't insisted on coming himself,

25:44.580 --> 25:46.640
I would have wiped them all out by now.

25:47.590 --> 25:48.720
Stop talking nonsense.

25:48.720 --> 25:49.380
Get to work.

25:58.680 --> 26:00.340
May I know your name, brother?

26:00.720 --> 26:01.780
My surname is Qing,

26:02.140 --> 26:03.270
and my given name is Long.

26:03.270 --> 26:04.030
Qing Long.

26:06.240 --> 26:07.640
That's an uncommon name.

26:08.750 --> 26:09.510
Sounds like

26:11.000 --> 26:12.030
an alias.

26:12.510 --> 26:13.550
Fake or real—

26:13.960 --> 26:15.090
what does it matter?

26:15.480 --> 26:16.230
If you're

26:16.850 --> 26:18.160
taking the straight path,

26:18.160 --> 26:19.090
there's a price.

26:19.590 --> 26:21.450
If you're taking the shadow path,

26:21.880 --> 26:23.840
there's another price.

26:24.610 --> 26:27.000
Which path are you on, brother?

26:30.920 --> 26:31.790
This item.

26:34.790 --> 26:36.000
The tung oil on it

26:36.040 --> 26:38.640
is used for transporting
military equipment.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.720
I suppose those girls being sold

26:40.720 --> 26:42.550
are just a cover for something else.

26:42.550 --> 26:45.550
Your real business
is smuggling military equipment.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.710
Should I just run off on my own…

27:04.710 --> 27:06.170
Is that really a good idea?

27:06.200 --> 27:07.570
He did save me after all.

27:09.080 --> 27:10.050
Forget it, forget it.

27:10.050 --> 27:11.850
He probably has a way out anyway.

27:12.160 --> 27:13.090
Where did she go?

27:17.720 --> 27:18.520
Not on my side.

27:19.550 --> 27:21.010
Keep searching. Let's go.

27:44.640 --> 27:45.350
Why

27:46.480 --> 27:47.480
are they all dead?

27:52.830 --> 27:56.090
Those people outside
aren't real canal workers, are they?

27:56.350 --> 27:57.310
Who exactly are you?

27:57.310 --> 27:58.720
The real ferry officials and canal workers

27:58.720 --> 28:00.250
were killed by you long ago.

28:00.480 --> 28:02.210
You are Prince Changsha's man.

28:02.400 --> 28:05.350
Were those repeating crossbows
that harmed the soldiers of the Beifu Army

28:05.350 --> 28:08.150
all transported from here
to the northern border?

28:14.550 --> 28:15.680
Could you be...

28:16.510 --> 28:17.240
Xiao...

28:17.240 --> 28:17.880
Xiao

28:18.830 --> 28:19.350
Wu

28:20.480 --> 28:21.070
yi.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.610
I'm here to save you!

28:34.750 --> 28:35.960
Sorry, I missed.

28:36.480 --> 28:38.140
You're just causing trouble.

28:42.750 --> 28:45.070
You... You know martial arts?

29:03.640 --> 29:04.640
Stop pretending.

29:04.960 --> 29:06.020
Still pretending?

29:17.550 --> 29:18.380
I'm not pretending.

29:18.380 --> 29:19.580
You're not a merchant

29:19.580 --> 29:20.950
and you're not a good person either.

29:20.950 --> 29:23.200
To think I even wanted to
save you just now.

29:23.200 --> 29:24.600
-How dare you...
-Get up!

29:25.650 --> 29:26.510
I'm telling you,

29:26.510 --> 29:27.910
I poisoned the crossbow.

29:28.960 --> 29:30.030
I have the antidote.

29:30.030 --> 29:30.720
Let me go.

29:31.070 --> 29:32.030
Get up.

29:37.270 --> 29:38.110
If I wanted you dead,

29:38.110 --> 29:40.240
you wouldn't have survived until now.

29:43.550 --> 29:45.150
Tell me, where are you going?

29:45.640 --> 29:46.570
I'll see you off.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.400
Thanks, but no thanks.

29:49.830 --> 29:50.830
I'll go by myself.

29:58.240 --> 29:58.960
I'm going

29:59.780 --> 30:00.440
to Yanzhou.

30:02.270 --> 30:02.960
For what?

30:04.450 --> 30:05.850
I'm going to get married.

30:05.880 --> 30:07.190
Did you see those boxes I brought?

30:07.190 --> 30:08.590
Those are my dowry items.

30:10.240 --> 30:11.960
How did your parents arrange

30:11.960 --> 30:13.400
such a distant marriage for you?

30:13.400 --> 30:15.510
My parents treat me very badly.

30:15.720 --> 30:18.070
They're forcing me
to marry some old widower.

30:18.070 --> 30:21.200
You know what he's like—old, ugly,

30:21.200 --> 30:22.240
and never bathes.

30:22.400 --> 30:24.600
And all he does every day is kill people.

30:26.030 --> 30:27.570
There's someone that disgusting?

30:27.570 --> 30:28.330
Of course.

30:29.480 --> 30:31.590
That's why I'm going to Yanzhou
to find my cousin.

30:31.590 --> 30:34.240
My cousin is handsome and brilliant.

30:35.000 --> 30:35.750
So,

30:36.650 --> 30:38.000
you are running away from your marriage.

30:38.000 --> 30:38.720
Exactly.

30:39.000 --> 30:40.200
If I really married that old widower,

30:40.200 --> 30:41.860
my whole life would be ruined.

30:42.750 --> 30:43.270
Good.

30:44.550 --> 30:45.270
Very good.

30:45.880 --> 30:47.350
Let's go find a boat.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.270
Are you going to kill people again?

30:49.270 --> 30:51.000
They are not good people anyway.

30:51.000 --> 30:52.590
But those boatmen don't know anything.

30:52.590 --> 30:53.750
They're just here to help.

30:53.750 --> 30:55.240
There are no innocent people
in this world.

30:55.240 --> 30:56.790
I believe that in this world,

30:56.790 --> 30:58.150
no one wants to be a bad person.

30:58.150 --> 31:00.110
They were also tricked into coming here.

31:00.110 --> 31:02.170
How do we leave without killing them?

31:04.370 --> 31:05.030
I have an idea.

31:05.030 --> 31:05.640
Follow me.

31:19.510 --> 31:20.160
Wait.

31:26.110 --> 31:27.040
Are you new here?

31:30.150 --> 31:32.350
Yes, we are new here.

31:37.280 --> 31:39.240
By the way, the ferry official
is looking for you.

31:39.240 --> 31:41.110
The ferry official is looking for us? Why?

31:41.110 --> 31:42.440
I don't know, but it's urgent.

31:42.440 --> 31:43.100
Go quickly.

31:43.400 --> 31:44.880
Yes, it's urgent.

31:47.230 --> 31:47.760
Let's go.

32:07.110 --> 32:08.240
We have to kill them anyway.

32:08.240 --> 32:09.830
I don't know why Young Lord Xiao

32:09.830 --> 32:11.350
is playing along with this scheme.

32:11.350 --> 32:12.840
He's probably afraid of scaring Lady Xie.

32:12.840 --> 32:14.070
Then what should we do?

32:14.070 --> 32:15.270
Kill them one by one as they come in.

32:15.270 --> 32:16.600
How long will that take?

32:17.160 --> 32:18.240
Is Young Lord Xiao on the boat?

32:18.240 --> 32:18.720
He left.

32:19.920 --> 32:21.650
Then let's kill them together.

32:24.640 --> 32:26.300
Soldiers of Prince Changsha,

32:26.830 --> 32:28.690
your leader has been killed by me!

32:28.960 --> 32:29.590
Come out.

33:22.400 --> 33:23.730
Here is a new one for you.

33:24.270 --> 33:27.130
Consider it a thank-you gift
for saving me just now.

33:31.100 --> 33:32.560
This thing is not durable.

33:33.030 --> 33:34.550
If it were used on the battlefield,

33:34.550 --> 33:36.000
it would get people killed.

33:36.000 --> 33:37.720
Who said it's for the battlefield?

33:37.720 --> 33:41.650
It's for noble lords to use
as decoration during hunting and banquets.

33:42.640 --> 33:43.370
Decoration?

33:43.750 --> 33:44.440
Yes.

33:44.880 --> 33:46.530
Few young nobles are good at hunting,

33:46.530 --> 33:48.110
but they want to pretend they are,

33:48.110 --> 33:50.790
so they compete to see
whose crossbow looks the finest.

33:50.790 --> 33:52.790
That's why I chose this kind of wood.

33:52.830 --> 33:54.320
If it were to be used on the battlefield,

33:54.320 --> 33:55.180
it would require poplar wood

33:55.180 --> 33:57.150
and be reinforced
with dark iron and ox horn.

33:57.150 --> 33:59.410
It's a lethal weapon on the battlefield,

33:59.440 --> 34:01.570
but in the capital, it's just for show?

34:01.920 --> 34:03.000
That's what the buyer asked for.

34:03.000 --> 34:04.070
What could I do?

34:06.090 --> 34:06.850
Do you still want it or not?

34:06.850 --> 34:08.250
If not, give it back to me.

34:22.440 --> 34:23.969
Good thing it's not broken.

34:25.440 --> 34:26.810
It's a gift for your cousin?

34:26.810 --> 34:27.670
Don't touch it.

34:32.320 --> 34:34.630
Have you even met the man

34:34.960 --> 34:36.560
your parents picked for you?

34:37.960 --> 34:39.690
He's old, ugly, and a murderer.

34:40.190 --> 34:41.650
I wouldn't want to see him.

34:43.420 --> 34:44.820
Rumors might not be true.

34:47.530 --> 34:48.489
I'm not stupid.

34:50.670 --> 34:51.330
You're not?

34:53.030 --> 34:55.360
I saw him kill many people
with my own eyes,

34:55.550 --> 34:56.010
just...

35:00.480 --> 35:01.940
Just like you did earlier.

35:03.360 --> 35:04.630
I did that to save you.

35:05.480 --> 35:06.630
But if I hadn't stopped you,

35:06.630 --> 35:08.490
you would have killed all of them.

35:09.480 --> 35:10.550
You know martial arts,

35:10.550 --> 35:12.190
but martial arts should be
used to protect the weak,

35:12.190 --> 35:13.650
not to kill people at will.

35:16.360 --> 35:18.160
I didn't expect someone your age

35:18.230 --> 35:19.430
to have such insight.

35:20.280 --> 35:22.550
Is that why you saved people
several times?

35:22.550 --> 35:23.880
You saved that orphan girl,

35:23.880 --> 35:25.340
and even wanted to save me.

35:26.230 --> 35:27.000
Pity.

35:27.670 --> 35:28.800
I failed to save one,

35:28.880 --> 35:29.610
and the other

35:30.070 --> 35:31.530
didn't need my help at all.

35:32.110 --> 35:34.030
But she bit the hand that fed her
and betrayed you.

35:34.030 --> 35:35.760
She was just trying to survive.

35:37.590 --> 35:38.790
You don't resent her?

35:42.670 --> 35:44.110
I'm still perfectly alive,

35:44.110 --> 35:45.570
while she is already dead.

35:45.760 --> 35:47.090
What is there to resent?

35:47.360 --> 35:48.890
You're quite open-minded.

35:51.440 --> 35:53.500
It's different from what I imagined.

35:53.950 --> 35:54.460
What?

35:58.510 --> 35:59.170
We're here.

36:00.360 --> 36:01.020
We're here?

36:02.190 --> 36:03.450
Is Yanzhou this close?

36:04.000 --> 36:06.260
When did I ever say
I was going to Yanzhou?

36:16.750 --> 36:17.140
I...

36:19.680 --> 36:21.210
Why am I back in the capital?

36:21.260 --> 36:23.150
Take her back to
the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

36:23.150 --> 36:23.480
Yes.

36:24.440 --> 36:25.150
You know me?

36:26.850 --> 36:27.980
Who exactly are you?

36:29.360 --> 36:30.190
Lady Xie,

36:30.630 --> 36:32.490
we will see each other again soon.

36:34.710 --> 36:35.230
Xie?

36:49.000 --> 36:49.510
He...

36:50.360 --> 36:50.890
Who is he?

36:58.400 --> 36:59.660
Why are you still here?

37:00.400 --> 37:01.880
Didn't I tell you to go to Xiyue Pavilion

37:01.880 --> 37:03.680
and the East Gate to look for her?

37:04.480 --> 37:05.550
Hurry, go!

37:06.710 --> 37:07.320
Yes.

37:09.760 --> 37:11.220
What's with these people?

37:16.280 --> 37:17.030
Darling,

37:17.920 --> 37:20.180
you're still drinking tea so leisurely.

37:20.190 --> 37:21.110
Yao Yao is missing.

37:21.110 --> 37:22.880
Why aren't you anxious at all?

37:23.400 --> 37:24.440
When it was time to discipline her,

37:24.440 --> 37:26.110
you spoiled her rotten.

37:27.150 --> 37:28.230
Is it a bit too late

37:28.670 --> 37:29.960
to be anxious now?

37:29.980 --> 37:31.460
If Yao Yao really ran away,

37:32.000 --> 37:33.260
then this marriage...

37:33.670 --> 37:35.630
This is disobeying an imperial edict.

37:35.630 --> 37:36.920
So what?

37:37.720 --> 37:39.640
This isn't my first time.

37:39.810 --> 37:42.210
Marrying you was also disobeying an edict.

37:44.440 --> 37:45.190
Besides,

37:46.290 --> 37:47.290
we won't lose her.

37:48.110 --> 37:50.800
Have you always had someone following her?

37:51.230 --> 37:52.360
Madam!

37:53.070 --> 37:54.330
Young Lady has returned.

37:54.330 --> 37:54.990
She's back?

37:55.030 --> 37:56.490
Someone brought her back.

37:57.150 --> 37:58.210
That's wonderful.

38:00.630 --> 38:02.360
Father! Mother!

38:02.450 --> 38:03.710
-Yao Yao!
-Let go of me!

38:03.750 --> 38:05.750
-Yao Yao.
-Letl Xiao Wuyi come to me!

38:06.710 --> 38:08.020
Father, Mother.

38:10.370 --> 38:12.330
Yao Yao, did I hear that right?

38:12.990 --> 38:15.110
Did you mean Young Lord Xiao?

38:15.760 --> 38:16.280
Yes.

38:16.440 --> 38:18.300
Who else could it be but Xiao Wuyi?

38:18.480 --> 38:19.590
I should have recognized that

38:19.590 --> 38:21.190
murderous bastard earlier!

38:21.670 --> 38:22.670
And he even told me

38:22.840 --> 38:24.440
that rumors might not be true.

38:24.440 --> 38:25.190
Hypocrite!

38:25.710 --> 38:26.920
How could he pretend for so long?

38:26.920 --> 38:28.590
It seems he's even worse than the rumors.

38:28.590 --> 38:30.190
Grand Tutor. Your Highness.

38:30.780 --> 38:31.910
Young Lord Xiao said

38:32.150 --> 38:33.920
the Empress Dowager's bestowed marriage
is a state affair.

38:33.920 --> 38:35.960
If Lady Xie continues to act recklessly,

38:35.960 --> 38:37.760
it will bring disaster
to your entire family.

38:37.760 --> 38:39.930
Please think twice.

38:39.960 --> 38:41.760
He dares to threaten my parents?

38:42.560 --> 38:43.290
You tell him,

38:43.420 --> 38:44.050
no way!

38:44.880 --> 38:47.510
Young Lord Xiao said if Lady Xie
wants to escape the marriage,

38:47.510 --> 38:48.740
she needs to
practice her martial arts more.

38:48.740 --> 38:49.340
He...

38:52.410 --> 38:53.550
Yao Yao!

38:54.000 --> 38:54.460
Yao Yao!

38:55.630 --> 38:56.630
The Prince Changsha's private troops

38:56.630 --> 38:58.230
secretly controlled Jiankang Ferry

38:58.230 --> 38:59.510
and smuggled people and goods.

38:59.510 --> 39:02.000
Later, they were controlled
by Prince Jing'an's Mansion's men.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.720
I have been secretly
protecting Young Lady.

39:03.720 --> 39:05.190
Recently, it's rumored in the capital

39:05.190 --> 39:09.550
that Young Lord Xiao took beautiful concubines
and dancers to his hot spring villa.

39:09.550 --> 39:11.760
He is quite interesting.

39:12.800 --> 39:13.800
You may leave now.

39:14.030 --> 39:14.590
Yes.

39:16.110 --> 39:17.670
Darling!

39:20.460 --> 39:21.720
Who are you talking to?

39:22.360 --> 39:23.000
No one.

39:24.760 --> 39:25.680
Yao Yao is having a nightmare.

39:25.680 --> 39:26.760
Come up and see her.

39:28.680 --> 39:29.150
Come.

39:36.070 --> 39:36.760
Don't kill!

39:40.840 --> 39:42.710
She always feels restricted at home

39:42.710 --> 39:44.310
and thinks the world is vast.

39:44.360 --> 39:48.000
Little does she know, outside the capital,
the people are already suffering.

39:48.000 --> 39:49.530
She has a passionate heart,

39:49.960 --> 39:51.960
but she can't even protect herself.

39:52.150 --> 39:54.800
This trip must have been
a huge blow to her.

39:55.110 --> 39:55.670
No.

39:56.400 --> 39:58.200
Young Lord Xiao already knows

39:58.760 --> 40:00.110
that Yao Yao ran away from the marriage.

40:00.110 --> 40:02.240
And he even had someone bring her back.

40:02.800 --> 40:03.880
This is a warning.

40:04.840 --> 40:07.800
It seems Yao Yao has to marry him.

40:09.630 --> 40:11.230
With military power in hand,

40:12.060 --> 40:15.720
even the Emperor and Empress Dowager
have to avoid his sharp edge.

40:27.510 --> 40:28.310
Wipe it clean.

40:35.510 --> 40:36.370
Your Highness,

40:37.030 --> 40:39.150
al the hidden troops
at the warehouse and ferry

40:39.150 --> 40:40.280
have been wiped out.

40:40.400 --> 40:42.530
From today on, everything is as usual.

40:43.230 --> 40:44.690
Nothing has changed here.

40:45.000 --> 40:45.800
I understand.

40:46.230 --> 40:48.430
I won't let the Prince Changsha notice.

40:49.070 --> 40:50.200
From the looks of it,

40:50.550 --> 40:52.840
Lady Xie doesn't seem to be conspiring
with the Prince Changsha.

40:52.840 --> 40:54.440
It's more like she's being used.

40:54.440 --> 40:55.440
I also don't think she is

40:55.440 --> 40:56.420
smart enough for that.

40:56.420 --> 40:56.820
No.

40:57.510 --> 41:00.230
I mean Lady Xie is a kindhearted person.

41:01.840 --> 41:02.900
In troubled times,

41:03.590 --> 41:06.960
even kindhearted people
can harm themselves and others.

41:09.190 --> 41:11.760
How could he be Xiao Wuyi?

41:13.630 --> 41:15.440
My Lady, just eat a little.

41:15.840 --> 41:17.770
You haven't eaten anything today.

41:18.710 --> 41:19.770
I have no appetite.

41:20.590 --> 41:22.000
You were unconscious for three days.

41:22.000 --> 41:23.070
You are still weak.

41:23.590 --> 41:24.850
If you don't rest well,

41:25.400 --> 41:27.260
you'll be the one to suffer later.

41:27.670 --> 41:28.840
Just let me suffer.

41:28.920 --> 41:31.380
These are sweet cakes
with osmanthus honey.

41:31.510 --> 41:34.570
It's Madam Ruan's latest recipe
from Miaoshan Bakery.

41:36.150 --> 41:37.280
That's more like it.

41:41.720 --> 41:42.320
Nanxing,

41:43.340 --> 41:44.800
why are you hiding from me?

41:46.050 --> 41:47.450
What's that in your hand?

41:49.800 --> 41:50.630
This is

41:51.560 --> 41:53.510
a gift from the Heir of Prince Jing'an.

41:53.510 --> 41:55.190
Her Highness asked me
to bring it to you.

41:55.190 --> 41:57.590
What good things
could he possibly give me?

42:08.120 --> 42:10.690
Xiao Wuyi!
